rows.label: tlk70000002_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Today we have celebration
for accolade of new Iira
knight, with 10% off sale!

rows.label: tlk70000002_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh dear! It friend custome- Ah,
no, what say! Friend knight!

rows.label: tlk70000002_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Not trying to cash in on happy
feeling of big event, OK? Just
want to mark occasion, OK?

rows.label: tlk70000002_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Mo? OK to carry on? Should
celebrate even more? Friend
knight such big-hearted!

rows.label: tlk70000002_03_msg0006
rows.name:
OK! Then let's have 20% off before
change mind! Mo! Roll up, roll up!
